title: Celebrating 40 years of the American Association of Nurse Practitioners: Honoring the legacy of its journal.
summary: This editorial briefly describes the history of the Journal of the American Association of Nurse Practitioners (NPs) as we join in the 40th year celebration of representing NPs and serving the health care needs of our patients....
